{"id":476363,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":1}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"104","ytitle":"","mtitle":"《红领巾》","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"(选自彩色剪纸片)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1966\\06\\6661040901.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>一、小红见特务快逃到海边，连忙吹起海螺报警。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1966\\06\\6661040902.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>二、三个妄想脱逃的特务在我民兵包围下全部就擒。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1966\\06\\6661040903.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三、民兵们赞扬小红的机智勇敢和不怕牺牲的精神。海旺替小红戴上红领中，说她是毛主席的好孩子。</FONT>"}]}